OL,3,CWhy did Labour U-turn on its #28bn
OL,4,Cgreen spending plan?
OL,6,FLabour has on environmental projects
OL,7,Fin a major U-turn, after months of
OL,8,Funcertainty.
OL,10,FShadow Chancellor Rachel Reeves first
OL,11,Fannounced the party's pledge to spend
OL,12,Fan extra #28 billion per year on green
OL,13,Finvestment at Labour's party
OL,14,Fconference in September 2021.
OL,16,FBut where did the figure come from and
OL,17,Fwhat does this U-turn mean?
OL,19,FWhat was the money going to be for?
