OL,3,CWhy did Labour U-turn on its #28bn
OL,4,Cgreen spending plan?
OL,6,FMs Reeves said a Labour government
OL,7,Fwould "invest in good jobs in the
OL,8,Fgreen industries of the future", with
OL,9,Finvestment in areas ranging from giga-
OL,10,Ffactories for electric vehicle
OL,11,Fbatteries and offshore wind turbines,
OL,12,Fto insulating homes, planting trees
OL,13,Fand building flood defences.
OL,15,FAt the same conference in 2021, Labour
OL,16,Fleader Sir Keir Starmer pledged the
OL,17,Fparty would insulate 19 million homes
OL,18,Fover 10 years.
