OL,3,CWhy did Labour U-turn on its #28bn
OL,4,Cgreen spending plan?
OL,6,FWhat is the plan now?
OL,8,FThe green prosperity plan still has a
OL,9,Fcommitment to clean power by 2030,
OL,10,Fwith #8.3 billion pledged for planned
OL,11,Fpublic energy company Great British
OL,12,FEnergy to invest in the sector.
OL,14,FThere is also a national wealth fund
OL,15,Ffor investing in clean technology from
OL,16,Fgreen steel to giga-factories, with
OL,17,Finvestment of #7.3 billion, and #500
OL,18,Fmillion a year to boost jobs and
OL,19,Finvestment in industrial communities.
