OL,3,CWhy did Labour U-turn on its #28bn
OL,4,Cgreen spending plan?
OL,6,FThe party has blamed the Conservatives
OL,7,Ffor "crashing the economy" and
OL,8,FChancellor Jeremy Hunt's "plans to
OL,9,F'max out' the country's credit card",
OL,10,Fsaying it would not be possible to
OL,11,Freach the previous commitment of #28
OL,12,Fbillion a year.
OL,14,FLabour has also been determined to
OL,15,Fcast itself as economically
OL,16,Fresponsible, and has said all spending
OL,17,Fwould be subject to a set of fiscal
OL,18,Frules to not borrow for day-to-day
OL,19,Fspending and get debt down.
